anner<br />\n下面就放數據<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f30a259a74f332d939e94116b074f470da5815a","tid":1568671,"uid":101963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:06:42.000Z","msg":"對付藍絲應該借力打力，順水推舟<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1568616\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1568616</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}